Subject: Unconstrained delegation
Description: Despite multiple Ping Castle runs and adjustments, 8 accounts still show unconstrained delegation. We've applied the same changes as other accounts, but some remain on the list for unknown reasons.
Next_Steps__c: Wait for customer to test what I sent and send information required.
Solution_Comment__c:
Symptom
accounts showing unconstrained delegation.


Resolution
 Explained that they will need to review each account and verify if they have any sort of delegation applied. Then they should remove or restrict it appropriately. 
Customer asked to close the case and will be back if needed.
